text.tspan: Share of marriages in England and Wales that ended in divorce
The percentage of marriages in England and Wales ending in divorce by duration and year of marriage.
Data source: UK Office for National Statistics (2024)
Note: Marriage cohorts are shown by year. For example, the "After 5 years" data point for 2017 reflects the share of marriages that took place
in 2017 and ended in divorce by 2022.
